metadata.name: DEEP CONNECTION
metadata.description:
"Man and nature are deeply related and cannot be separated from each other. Human being depends on nature for their subsistence and at the same time having to protect nature to last forever, because when nature disappears from the earth, it is possible that human being cannot alive in the world"

1/1 edition, 4500 x 6300 pixels, 300 dpi.
Digital Hand Drawn, Pop Surrealism Art.
